snippet.title: Delivery from the Pain - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Survival-themed apocalyptic horror game Delivery from the Pain is heading to Play Station 4/5 and Nintendo Switch this June 9th, developed by DigiPotato Studio, published by indienova.You will play as a survivor, trying to find a way to escape in a city of zombies.

https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/delivery-from-the-pain-switch/
